1
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:22,160
Ms. Wu.

2
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:23,160
You know,

3
00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:24,680
the only person who can make my buddy

4
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:26,000
so nervous

5
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:28,039
is Ms. Jian.

6
00:01:29,039 --> 00:01:29,760
Of course.

7
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:33,720
When are you planning to get married?

8
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,440
It's up to Lu Fan.

9
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,280
That must be Xiao Qi.

10
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:01,160
He's quite young.

11
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,440
Beautiful lady,

12
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:14,640
would you do me the honor
of being my dance partner tonight?

13
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:16,700
Then I'm all yours tonight, Mr. Xiao.

14
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,970
Black is the color of mourning.

15
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:48,440
It suits you.

16
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:50,480
A life-and-death friendship

17
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:53,010
deserves to be treated carefully,
of course.

18
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:55,280
Why did you drink when your hand hurt?

19
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,960
Pain is also worth remembering,

20
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,720
isn't it?

21
00:03:23,079 --> 00:03:23,720
Okay.

22
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:32,360
Fan.

23
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:35,680
Now Huishan has another tough guy.

24
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:39,320
If you and Xiao Qi were to have a fight,

25
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,760
who would win?

26
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,490
Not interested.

27
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,560
I'm sorry, Su Xia.

28
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,200
I didn't mean it.

29
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:06,720
Here,

30
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,720
I'll drink this to apologize to you.

31
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,600
What are you doing?

32
00:04:17,880 --> 00:04:19,209
I'm apologizing to her.

33
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,280
Ms. Wu,

34
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:28,240
I heard the Wu family
is planning a marriage alliance.

35
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,500
What do you think of me?

36
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:33,010
Are you crazy?
Why are you saying this now?

37
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:35,000
Since you don't like words,

38
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,200
I'll just use actions.

39
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,960
I'll make our relationship a done deal.

40
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:39,360
From now on, you are my fiancée.

41
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,760
Let's get along well.

42
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,720
Let go of me!

43
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,520
I'm sorry.

44
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,440
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

45
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:48,409
That's more like it.

46
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,120
Su Xia, I'm sorry.

47
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:58,840
What did I tell you? People can change,

48
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,930
as long as you use the right method.

49
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,170
Where are you going?

50
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,120
I'm drunk.

51
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:06,960
I need to throw up.

52
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,920
Why did you leave so suddenly?

53
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:33,850
Are you unhappy?

54
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:35,920
I'm not.

55
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,560
I just feel a little sick.

56
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,600
Why do you feel sick?

57
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:47,280
Are you... angry?

58
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:51,480
Are you crazy?

59
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:53,320
You're hurting me.

60
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,659
It seems you are really angry.

61
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,280
Why are you reacting so strongly?

62
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:59,240
Are you jealous?

63
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:10,120
You are exactly like your sister.

64
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,360
Am I?

65
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:13,720
But people say,

66
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,840
like father, like son.

67
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,760
Are you like Uncle Lu?

68
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,060
What's wrong with you?

69
00:06:21,840 --> 00:06:23,170
Don't mention him to me.

70
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:28,440
I'm just trying to understand you again.

71
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:30,040
Shut up.

72
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:31,700
I don't want to.

73
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,960
Don't have anything to do with me anymore,

74
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:36,680
okay?

75
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,520
Is it that you don't want to,

76
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:44,650
or you don't dare to?

77
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,480
Don't push me too far.

78
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:56,280
Then let's see.

79
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,520
Psychopath.

80
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:41,200
You witch!

81
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,880
Thank you all for coming.

82
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:45,760
I hope I can learn a lot from you.

83
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:46,840
No problem.

84
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,400
How dare you come back?

85
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:00,280
I think you have a death wish.

86
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,000
Ms. Wu.

87
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,320
When you were apologizing to me,

88
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,920
you weren't this arrogant.

89
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:09,760
Are you showing off to me

90
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:11,620
that you have a man backing you up?

91
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,400
Bitch!

92
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,090
How dare you fight back?

93
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:25,920
First you seduced Xiao Qi, and now Lu Fan.

94
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:26,720
Do you have to be

95
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,360
as cheap as your sister?

96
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,760
Does Jian Xi know

97
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:35,280
that you covet her fiancé?

98
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:39,039
You're laughing?

99
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:41,090
How dare you laugh? Stop laughing!

100
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,520
But,

101
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:48,760
seeing you act like a dog

102
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,440
around Jian Xi,

103
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:53,040
just to steal another glance
at my brother,

104
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:55,000
it's hard for me not to laugh.

105
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,840
You are obviously a bitch.

106
00:08:58,040 --> 00:08:59,770
Why are you acting so innocent?

107
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:00,880
You bitch!

108
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,360
Let me tell you,

109
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:06,040
Lu Fan is definitely mine.

110
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:09,840
Beat her up!

111
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,560
Mr. Lu! Mr. Lu!

112
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:30,880
Mr. Lu, please let me explain.

113
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:32,200
Mr. Lu! Mr. Lu!

114
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:44,760
Lu Fan!

115
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,320
Hang in there.

116
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,090
Does it hurt?

117
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,560
No. I'm used to it.

118
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:28,460
Then why did you call for help?

119
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:31,320
But if I hadn't,

120
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:32,880
I would have died.

121
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,920
I know them too well.

122
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,240
Some people

123
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:38,680
won't realize the evil they've done

124
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,880
just because they grow older.

125
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:43,560
They will only get worse

126
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:45,060
if they go unpunished.

127
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:46,240
Okay.

128
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:50,560
Next time you call for help,
go to someone else.

129
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:56,600
But I never thought of
going to anyone else.

130
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:57,920
In that moment,

131
00:10:58,640 --> 00:11:01,160
the only person I thought of was you.
